OL,3,CGreens confident as counting underway
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton
OL,6,FThe Greens appeared confident that
OL,7,Fthey were in the lead as counting was
OL,8,Funderway in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FZack Polanski's party said "things are
OL,12,Ffeeling positive", while Labour
OL,13,Fsources suggested the Greens "have
OL,14,Fbeen able to turn out support" in the
OL,15,Fcontest.
OL,26,@sD@\OUtD@QO]uD@^OUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
