OL,3,CGreens confident as counting underway
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton
OL,6,FLabour Party chairwoman Anna Turley
OL,7,Fearlier said she was "really
OL,8,Foptimistic" about Labour's chances,
OL,9,Fbut cautioned: "Of course incumbent
OL,10,Fgovernment always find it difficult to
OL,11,Ffight by-elections."
OL,13,FMore than a thousand Labour activists
OL,14,Fwere out across the constituency and
OL,15,Fspoke to more voters than on any
OL,16,Fprevious by-election polling day,
OL,17,Faccording to party sources.
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@KO]qD@POUsD@TO]
