OL,3,CGreens confident as counting underway
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton
OL,6,FThe loss of the once-safe Greater
OL,7,FManchester constituency would renew
OL,8,Fspeculation about the Prime Minister's
OL,9,Fposition, which has come under
OL,10,Fpressure from the Lord Peter Mandelson
OL,11,Fscandal, a slew of departures from No
OL,12,F10 and Labour's plummeting popularity.
OL,14,FThe decision to block potential
OL,15,Fleadership rival Andy Burnham from
OL,16,Frunning would also likely come under
OL,17,Ffire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
