PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772175649
OL,3,CGreens confident as counting underway
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton
OL,6,FLabour lost the only other Westminster
OL,7,Fby-election since the 2024 general
OL,8,Felection, in Runcorn and Helsby, to
OL,9,FNigel Farage's Reform UK last May.
OL,11,FGorton and Denton was seen as a tight
OL,12,Frace between Reform's Matt Goodwin,
OL,13,FLabour and the Greens.
OL,15,FTurnout on Thursday was 47.6%, broadly
OL,16,Fin line with the 47.8% recorded in
OL,17,F2024.
OL,19,FThe contest was triggered by former
OL,20,FLabour MP Andrew Gwynne standing down
OL,21,Ffor health reasons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
