OL,3,CGreens confident as counting underway
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised about people
OL,7,Fforcing relatives to vote in a certain
OL,8,Fway.
OL,10,FAfter polls closed, election observer
OL,11,Fgroup Democracy Volunteers warned it
OL,12,Fhad witnessed family voting ` an
OL,13,Fillegal practice where two voters use
OL,14,Fone polling booth and potentially
OL,15,Fdirect each other on voting ` in 68%
OL,16,Fof polling stations observed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772175649
OL,3,CGreens confident as counting underway
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton
OL,6,F"We rarely issue a report on the night
OL,7,Fof an election, but the data we have
OL,8,Fcollected today on family voting, when
OL,9,Fcompared to other recent by-elections,
OL,10,Fis extremely high," the group said.
OL,12,FLabour's Ms Turley said the report was
OL,13,F"extremely worrying and concerning",
OL,14,FReform's Mr Farage said it raised
OL,15,F"questions about the integrity of the
OL,16,Fdemocratic process in predominantly
OL,17,FMuslim areas", and Greens leader Mr
OL,18,FPolanski suggested he would back a
OL,19,Fprobe into the issue.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@SO]uD@AOUuD@cO]wD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
