OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772175649
OL,3,CGreens confident as counting underway
OL,4,Cin Gorton and Denton
OL,6,FManchester City Council said no issues
OL,7,Fhad been reported and said it was
OL,8,F"extremely disappointing" that
OL,9,FDemocracy Volunteers waited until
OL,10,Fafter the close of polls to make the
OL,11,Fclaims.
OL,13,FBut the group's director John Ault
OL,14,Ftold the Press Association that it "is
OL,15,Fa normal international standard not to
OL,16,Fissue a comment until after a voting
OL,17,Fhas finished" and that "we posed
OL,18,Fquestions about family voting in
OL,19,Fseveral polling stations".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@YO]vD@dOUyD@MO]yD@XOU{D@YO]
